{
  "id": "adv_bond_skr_01_04",
  "title": "川咲さくら4",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさん、mihoさん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "miho-san‚ miho-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "行かないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not going",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　まだ何も言ってませんよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? I haven't even said anything yet!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.433333683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "寮でパーティーをするから私にも来いって話でしょ？\nだから行かないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're going to tell me to come to a party at the dorm‚ right?\nSo‚ my answer is no",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.733333683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "え、一言も言ってないのに……\nみ、mihoさんってもしかしてエスパー……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ I didn't say a single word…\nmi-miho-san‚ are you by any chance an… esper?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.733333683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ？　バカなこと――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? Don't be ridic——",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7000012397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、秘密ってみんな一つくらい持ってると思います\n絶対言いませんから、こっそり私にだけ教えて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I think everyone has at least one secret\nI won't tell a soul‚ so please‚ just tell me in secret",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0666668891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "この事務所、朝からパーティーの話題ばかりだし――\nって、仮に秘密があっても貴方には言わないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The office has been full of talk about the party since morning——\nActually‚ even if I had a secret‚ I wouldn't tell you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9000002224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり……！　じゃあ、この件は私の心の中だけに\nしまっておきますね。mihoさんと私だけの秘密です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew it…! Then‚ I'll keep this tucked away\nonly in my heart. It's a secret between you and me‚ miho-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4000002224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私mihoさんのこと凄いと思います！\nそんな特別な能力があるのに、自慢もしないで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ I think you're truly amazing‚ miho-san!\nHaving such a special power and not even bragging about it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.6666668891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば千紗ちゃんと観たアクション映画の主人公も\n能力のこと、誰にも言えずに苦しんでました……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ the hero in the action movie I saw with Chisa\nsuffered because they couldn't tell anyone about their power…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.0666668891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさん！　もし、そのせいで辛いことがあったら\n私に相談して下さいね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "miho-san! If you ever have a hard time because of that‚\nplease come talk to me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.2000002224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "何を勝手に盛り上がって――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you getting so worked up about——",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9333335558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "私なんかが力になれるか分からないけど……\n精一杯応援します！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't know if I can be of much help‚ but…\nI'll support you with all my heart!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.833338642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "まずは今日、星見の寮に集合です！\n夜八時頃からパーティーを始めるので、待ってますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First of all‚ we're gathering at the Hoshimi dorm today!\nThe party starts around 8 PM‚ so I'll be waiting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.5333350817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "なんてったって私達\n秘密を共有する仲間ですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After all‚ we're\ncomrades who share a secret!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.6333350817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "（結局、おかしな勘違いをしたうえに）\n（一方的にパーティーに誘って去った……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（In the end‚ she made a weird misunderstanding‚）\n（and just left after unilaterally inviting me to a party…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.866668415,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3200.000667599994
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "（まさか……勘違いしたフリをしてパーティーへの）\n（誘いを押し切った？　さすがに考え過ぎ……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Wait… did she just pretend to misunderstand）\n（to push through the invitation? No‚ am I overthinking it…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.866668415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_04-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "（川咲さくら……やはり、底が見えないわね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Kawasaki Sakura… just as I thought‚ she's unfathomable）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9000017483,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}